# Summary
This documentation page explains how to integrate Amplitude cohorts with Twitter Ads to create targeted audiences for campaigns, including prerequisites, setup steps in Amplitude, required user identifiers (Device ID, Email, Handle, X ID, Phone Number), and the process for sending cohorts to Twitter Ads.

